texts.text: Several decorative block variants have names which describe them as chiseled. Each of these blocks shows a complex design, either abstract or a mob face. They share parallel crafting recipes which seem to "combine two slabs back into a full block" for each eligible stone type.

Chiseled Deepslate
Chiseled Nether Bricks, which shows a Wither Skeleton.
Chiseled Polished Blackstone, which shows a Piglin snout.
Chiseled Quartz Block
Chiseled Red Sandstone, which shows a Wither.
Chiseled Sandstone, which shows a Creeper.
Chiseled Stone Bricks.
Infested Chiseled Stone Bricks
